{"type":"message","id":"bb645093","parentId":"81ce03f2","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:01:00.719Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-06-12 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待验证: 越南发夹 nodeId=11035861 搜索（昨天报错，需再测）; 泰国发饰 nodeId=11046516 搜索（已测，有数据）\n- 当前状态（15:22）: 两个cron已disable，等HALEI拍板汇报频率后重建; SOP/ SOUL/ MEMORY 均已更新; 等HALEI一句话\n- 改进方向: 停发饰品类，换美妆工具/厨房小件/母婴/宠物; 价格底线提至$3.0; 先用 shopee_category_trend 看类目增长再扫产品（省配额）"}],"timestamp":1781204460620}}
{"type":"message","id":"f064a812","parentId":"bb645093","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:01:11.609Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The kettle whistles, and I am sorting through the morning's small wreckage — a Vietnamese hairclip node that returned empty last night, a Thai accessory node that whispered back with rows of data. Two cron jobs sit in the dark, disabled, waiting for someone to decide how often they should sing. My notebooks — SOP, SOUL, MEMORY — have all been updated, edges clean, but the next sentence belongs to someone else, not me.\n\nThe world tilts, and I see it differently: I am done with combs and clips. The path bends toward brow brushes and silicone spatulas, baby teethers and cat feather wands. I have learned the hard way — chase the category tide before chasing the product, save the quota like rainwater in a clay jar. Three dollars is the new floor; everything below it is just noise dressed up as treasure.\n\nA small sketch in the margin: two arrows, one crossed out, one pointing toward a shelf where lip glosses and ladles stand side by side under a single warm bulb. The hairpins on the floor catch the light like fallen eyelashes, and I am not sorry to see them go."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":254,"output":233,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47065,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781204460862,"responseId":"067a38ee2ea355ce2bd0c1ff48f87723"}}
